task.summary: Updated UI Fragment One, OnlineActivity, adding Firebase and pending Firebase Authentication
- Using Firebase Auth and Firebase Auth UI to build sign in, sign out funcs - Support Google sign-in and Facebook login - Update icon launcher app ...add some support libraries
- Fix log in and log out funcs using Firebase AuthUI
- get Track info from Intent Createchoser data uri using FFmpegMediaMetadataRetriever lib - upload Track info to Firebase realtime database, Track and Track Image to Firebase Storage
- upload fix bug v2: prevent duplicate new data upload

MESSAGE.value: Update UI Fragment One, OnlineActivity, adding Firebase and pending Firebase Authentication
Updated UI Fragment One, OnlineActivity, adding Firebase and pending Firebase Authentication
- Using Firebase Auth and Firebase Auth UI to build sign in, sign out funcs - Support Google sign-in and Facebook login - Update icon launcher app ...add some support libraries
- Fix log in and log out funcs using Firebase AuthUI
- get Track info from Intent Createchoser data uri using FFmpegMediaMetadataRetriever lib - upload Track info to Firebase realtime database, Track and Track Image to Firebase Storage
- upload fix bug v2: prevent duplicate new data upload
